  <div class="card-content">
    <h3 class="is-4 subtitle">Your Ember.js app needs say</h3>
    <p>
      Given an existing ember-app, we'll show you how to integrate the say-editor in it. Check out the
      <LinkTo @route="docs.deploy-as-addon">tutorial</LinkTo>
      <br> <br>
      To see a real-world implementation, check out
      <LinkTo
        @route="docs.implementations.from-repository"
        @models={{array "lblod" "app-gelinkt-notuleren"}}>Gelinkt Notuleren</LinkTo>. <br>
